<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Welcome to Register</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/register.css" />
    <script src="./js/register.js"></script>
    <!-- <script src="/server.js"></script> -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.js" integrity="sha256-H+K7U5CnXl1h5ywQfKtSj8PCmoN9aaq30gDh27Xc0jk=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <!-- 합쳐지고 최소화된 최신 CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <!-- 부가적인 테마 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.2/css/bootstrap-theme.min.css">
    <!-- 합쳐지고 최소화된 최신 자바스크립트 -->
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="notice">
      <%=name%>님 반갑습니다.<br>회원가입을 진행합니다.
    </div>
    <form method="post" id="register_form">
      <div class="form-group">
        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="id" name="registerID" placeholder="I  D" />
      </div>
      <div id="overlap_id">특수문자 + 영문 + 숫자의 조합으로 12자 이상으로 구성</div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <input type="password" class="form-control" id="pw" name="registerPW" placeholder="P  W" />
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <input type="password" class="form-control" id="confirm_pw" name="registerPW_confirm" placeholder="CONFIRM">
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <button id="btnSubmit" name="btnSubmit" type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">회원가입</button>
      </div>
    </form>
